    <item>
      <title>管理人面临费用压力，对冲基金初创企业数量减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/hedge-fund-startups-dwindle-as-managers-battle-pressure-on-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[规模接近 5 万亿美元的对冲基金行业正经历几十年来最艰难的一年，需要说服对费用敏感的投资者为新的市场参与者投入资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/hedge-fund-startups-dwindle-as-managers-battle-pressure-on-fees</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
